    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically fresh off the lot? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in flawless condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014not a scratch, no spills, and it smells like a dream inside. It drives like a cloud and looks even better in person. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
